# UI Test Account
#
# The account used by all subagents to log into the system under test.
# The test team has confirmed that concurrent sessions sharing the same
# account is safe — the system under test does NOT log out the older
# session on duplicate login. Therefore a single account is sufficient
# regardless of max_concurrent_subagents.
#
# Format: "username:password". Lines starting with # and blank lines
# are ignored. Only the first valid entry is used.
#
# Edited at deployment time, like gitlab.env. Read by scripts/load_ui_accounts.sh.

F100001:123456
